movies.title: Mayabazar
movies.description: The story revolves around the characters in the Hindu Epic The Mahabharata and is set in Dwaraka, the hometown of Lord Krishna.Arjuna's son Abhimanyu falls in love with Balarama's daughter Sasirekha. When the Pandavas lose their kingdom in the infamous game of dice to the Kauravas, Balarama promises his daughter's hand to Duryodhana's son,thereby breaking the promise made to Subhadra (Abhimanu's mother and Balarama's sister).The rest of the movie is how Bhima's son Ghatotkacha  uses his magic to help the lovers reunite.

movies.title: Gundamma Katha
movies.description: Gundamma, a rich widow, has one goal - to get her spoilt daughter married to a rich boy. She, however, treats her step daughter like a maid. Gundamma does not care about the step daughter's life or marriage. How two brothers, who are sons of a rich friend of Gundamma's husband, get married to the half-sisters and teach Gundamma a lesson forms the rest of the story.

movies.title: Harry Potter Film series
movies.description: The Harry Potter film series is a British film series based on the first seven Harry Potter books by English author JK Rowling . The series started in 2001 and was completed in 2011 and consists of eight full-length films. The last book, the seventh, has been filmed in two parts. The series has been supplemented with several prequels since 2016 , which are based on the book Fantastic Beasts and Where To Find Them .
